high_descs: Proceed to counter, turn right, proceed to counter, turn left to face counter with knife on it.
Pick up knife from edge of counter, in front of tomato and potato.
Turn around, proceed to table.  Turn left to face table.
Place knife, standing up, on right rim of plate to the left of the furthest left apple.
Pick up plate with knife on it.
Turn around, proceed to counter with microwave on it.
Place the plate with the knife on the counter, to the right of the microwave, directly in front of the horizontal fork.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife to a plate, place both on a counter.

high_descs: Move forward and then turn right, and face the counter on the left.
Pick up the knife from the front of the counter.
Carry the knife and turn to the left, then left again and face the table on the left side.
Place the knife on the plate in the center of the table.
Pick up the plate from the center of the table.
Take the plate and turn to the left and to the left again to locate the microwave.
Place the plate and knife on the counter, to the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and knife to the counter.

high_descs: Go forward to the front of the counter on the right of the sink.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the round wooden table on the other side.
Place the gray knife on the gray plate in front of the coffee machine.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it.
Turn around and go to the counter with the microwave.
Place the plate with knife on it on the counter in front of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with knife on it on the counter next to the microwave.
